# Task 2 - CRUD Operations using PHP & MySQL

## Overview

This project was developed as part of the ApexPlanet Web Development Internship. The objective of this task was to implement complete CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) functionality using PHP and MySQL.

## Features

### Create Operation

* Add new users through a registration form
* Store user details in MySQL database

### Read Operation

* Display all users in a responsive Bootstrap table
* Retrieve records dynamically from the database

### Update Operation

* Edit user details such as Name, Email, Phone, and Address
* Update records in the database

### Delete Operation

* Delete user records from the database

